1
00:00:06,020 --> 00:00:07,339
The new ambassador

2
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:08,980
is on the way.

3
00:00:18,060 --> 00:00:18,699
Miss Wu,

4
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:21,419
we heard you're here
to terminate your contract with Minghui.

5
00:00:21,420 --> 00:00:22,780
Is that true?

6
00:00:22,820 --> 00:00:23,699
Starting today,

7
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:25,859
I'm officially ending my contract
with Minghui.

8
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:27,780
Shouldn't you all be celebrating for me?

9
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:33,219
Mr. Shen,

10
00:00:33,220 --> 00:00:34,339
why are you willing

11
00:00:34,340 --> 00:00:36,139
to pay a high penalty

12
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,699
to help Miss Wu terminate the contract?

13
00:00:37,700 --> 00:00:40,060
Is this related to
Junlin Group's decision?

14
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,059
I'm helping Miss Wu Qing

15
00:00:42,060 --> 00:00:42,939
so that

16
00:00:42,940 --> 00:00:45,339
individuals or companies
with negative publicity

17
00:00:45,340 --> 00:00:47,059
won't affect

18
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:48,380
her future career.

19
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:11,060
Look! It's Su Mei.

20
00:01:13,260 --> 00:01:14,260
It really is.

21
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:21,460
Excuse me. Go after her.

22
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:46,700
Coming through.

23
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:47,979
Come on.

24
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:49,220
Hurry.

25
00:01:49,740 --> 00:01:50,740
Quick.

26
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:53,700
Excuse me.

27
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:56,820
Hurry up.

28
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,019
Ms. Su Mei,

29
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,899
are you here in Gang City

30
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,780
because of the recent rumors?

31
00:02:10,380 --> 00:02:13,940
I was invited by
Mr. Shen Gu and Ms. Xu Wanxin

32
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:17,060
to come to Gang City and sign
an endorsement deal with Minghui Group.

33
00:02:18,420 --> 00:02:19,580
Next question.

34
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,899
On behalf of Minghui Group,

35
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:28,540
welcome, Ms. Su Mei.

36
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:32,540
It's an honor.

37
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,940
Xu Wanxin.

38
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,580
You've really humbled yourself

39
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:38,939
and let Shen Gu's rumored lover

40
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:40,980
stand here on your turf.

41
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:52,019
Mr. Shen Hao,

42
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:53,819
you might want to watch your mouth.

43
00:02:53,820 --> 00:02:56,139
I wouldn't mind charging you
with defamation

44
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:57,380
to fix your problem.

45
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,010
What do you mean?

46
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:08,420
You want a photo with our Best Actress?

47
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,580
You're not worthy.

48
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:25,660
Please step back a little.

49
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:28,619
I don't want to be cropped out
this time.

50
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:30,820
You won't be this time.

51
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,729
Come a bit closer.

52
00:03:32,730 --> 00:03:33,920
Yes.

53
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:35,550
Look this way.

54
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:41,300
=Echoes of Gang City=

55
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:46,680
=Episode 15=
(Not a Love Rival, But an Ally)

56
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:48,259
Ladies and gentleman,

57
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:51,859
this is the endorsement contract
between Ms. Su and Minghui Group.

58
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:53,140
Please take a look.

59
00:04:01,780 --> 00:04:03,460
These terms

60
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,860
are extremely favorable to Minghui.

61
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:07,260
Ms. Su Mei,

62
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:09,140
are you sure about this?

63
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:10,340
Of course.

64
00:04:10,740 --> 00:04:11,940
It's our first meeting today.

65
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,579
Even though our names

66
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:16,139
have appeared together online
many times,

67
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:18,460
allow me to formally introduce myself.

68
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,060
Su Mei.

69
00:04:21,740 --> 00:04:22,860
Xu Wanxin.

70
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:26,020
Thank you for choosing Minghui.

71
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:29,059
We'll give this partnership

72
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,740
our full commitment.

73
00:04:30,790 --> 00:04:32,300
It's my honor.

74
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,820
The honor is mine too.

75
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:41,339
You two are way too slow.

76
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:44,700
It took you so long
to deliver the contract to my new boss.

77
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:47,980
This is my wedding gift, you know?

78
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:49,380
Right.

79
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:50,860
My bad.

80
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:57,380
You're not signed with any brand
right now, are you?

81
00:04:59,140 --> 00:05:00,300
You're signing me?

82
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:03,340
Minghui is signing you.

83
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:04,580
That's right.

84
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:07,819
Junlin may completely cut ties
with Minghui,

85
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:10,740
so they need
a most influential ambassador.

86
00:05:11,140 --> 00:05:12,219
That's why

87
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:16,260
he chose you to work with Minghui.

88
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:20,380
Thank you for the trust.

89
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:22,260
When do we sign?

90
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:26,580
That depends on
Lawyer Fang's efficiency.

91
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:30,060
I'm always efficient.

92
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:31,860
Fine.

93
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:34,060
I accept any terms.

94
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:36,180
Consider it my wedding gift.

95
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,060
Didn't expect to see this happen
to Shen Gu.

96
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,939
Thank you so much.

97
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,900
You showed up just in time and saved me.

98
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:53,780
No need.

99
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:59,860
You actually seem pretty happy
being the victim.

100
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:03,659
Alright.

101
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:04,819
We've talked enough.

102
00:06:04,820 --> 00:06:06,700
If we keep going, it'll be dark soon.

103
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:09,700
I'll leave
the advertisement shoot to you.

104
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,619
Nice to meet you,

105
00:06:15,620 --> 00:06:16,940
my new boss.

106
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:18,700
Look forward to working with you.

107
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:20,300
Stay in touch.

108
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:21,660
I'll walk you out.

109
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,900
Please stay.

110
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,180
No need.

111
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:33,060
I'll take Ms. Su Mei to dinner.

112
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,179
Mr. Xu,

113
00:06:55,180 --> 00:06:57,739
we've signed with Su Mei.

114
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:59,300
It was arranged by Shen Gu.

115
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:04,380
Seems like

116
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:06,900
I worried for nothing.

117
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,700
Shuyi,

118
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,140
it's my fault.

119
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:19,579
Half a month ago,

120
00:07:19,580 --> 00:07:22,059
I didn't get the lipstick myself.

121
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,780
I bought it at a high price.

122
00:07:24,220 --> 00:07:25,380
And a week ago,

123
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:27,380
I had an argument with someone.

124
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:29,339
It wasn't about academics.

125
00:07:29,340 --> 00:07:30,660
It's because

126
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:34,460
he likes you.

127
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,980
I got jealous.

128
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:39,460
And three days ago,

129
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,939
I ate your snacks

130
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:42,700
and blamed Qianmo.

131
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:46,060
Whatever you're mad about, I'll fix it.

132
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:48,060
Just please

133
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:50,580
don't ignore me.

134
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:53,539
I knew it.
I only ate one piece that day.

135
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:55,139
He insisted I had two

136
00:07:55,140 --> 00:07:56,659
and called me greedy.

137
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:58,459
You were so upset.

138
00:07:58,460 --> 00:08:00,299
You have no idea how delicious

139
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:02,219
the pastries his cousin brought
from Nanyang are.

140
00:08:02,220 --> 00:08:05,060
I even asked him
to save you a whole box.

141
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:09,340
Cousin?

142
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:11,259
When did his cousin come?

143
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:13,619
The day you got mad at Mr. Shen.

144
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,739
She came all the way
back from Nanyang

145
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:17,540
for your engagement.

146
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,140
Shuyi,

147
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:21,139
I was wrong. Can you...

148
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:22,300
Shen Gu,

149
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:25,659
no matter what happens in the future,
you have to tell me everything.

150
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,780
Got it?

151
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,660
Dummy.

152
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:34,700
Fine.

153
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:37,060
I was at fault too.

154
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:38,339
No.

155
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:39,740
It was my fault.

156
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:41,260
I forgive you.

157
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,700
As if I didn't exist.

158
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:48,100
I'm not mad anymore.

159
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,860
Boss, paparazzi.

160
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:10,740
Got it.

161
00:10:31,580 --> 00:10:32,900
Where are we going?

162
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:34,539
The market.

163
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:36,020
The paparazzi will find us.

164
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:42,620
Let them be.

165
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:50,800
Next time you hold my hand,
can you come up with a better excuse?

166
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:52,739
What do you want to eat?

167
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:54,460
What's your specialty?

168
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:57,660
West Lake Vinegar Fish.

169
00:10:57,820 --> 00:11:01,260
Sweet and Sour Pork Rib.
Spicy Vinegar Soy Sauce Duck.

170
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,620
I'll help you change it.

171
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,520
(Mustard greens, 12 yuan per 500g)

172
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:25,220
It doesn't look like
your first time cooking.

173
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:28,300
I used to cook for myself
when I was abroad.

174
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:31,220
I'm looking forward to it.

175
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:33,899
How much?

176
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,340
That'll be twenty.

177
00:11:37,020 --> 00:11:37,860
Thank you.

178
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:42,019
You'll get to taste

179
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:43,420
my cooking later.

180
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:48,899
Miss Xu,

181
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,820
can I give you another bouquet?

182
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:55,060
Mr. Shen, you really hold grudges.

183
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:10,300
I'll go cook now.

184
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:11,820
Mm.

185
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:34,260
I'll help.

186
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:42,540
I'll get your apron.

187
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:49,020
Let me help.

188
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:03,820
Were you mad that day

189
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:06,180
because you were jealous?

190
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:07,180
I wasn't.

191
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:10,860
No?

192
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:16,140
Then why did you throw away my flowers?

193
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:20,020
Because you didn't respect
our agreement.

194
00:14:24,020 --> 00:14:25,779
I've never treated what we have

195
00:14:25,780 --> 00:14:27,540
as just a contract.

196
00:14:30,890 --> 00:14:36,410
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

197
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:42,890
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

198
00:14:44,170 --> 00:14:49,650
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

199
00:14:50,770 --> 00:14:56,090
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

200
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:39,300
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

201
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:46,380
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

202
00:15:47,100 --> 00:15:52,460
♪You turn and look back at me♪

203
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:59,100
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

204
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:05,580
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

205
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:12,340
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

206
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:18,780
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

207
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:25,740
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

208
00:16:26,140 --> 00:16:33,100
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

209
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:38,900
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

210
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:45,939
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

211
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:48,819
♪The promise we made♪

212
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:52,499
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

213
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:59,099
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

214
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:05,500
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

215
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:12,219
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

216
00:17:12,220 --> 00:17:17,340
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

217
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:20,820
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
